{"tid":1777827,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[和理非入]有手足好俾心機剪咗條宣傳片，教你點支援勇武","createTime":"2019-12-10T13:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T14:09:14.000Z","uid":89974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7bd6befcc691b80177d67e28001347f62e00e039","tid":1777827,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">答案就係罷工！！！<br />\n和理非唔係廢物，唔係剩係可以遊行捐錢！<br />\n誠招所有被炒都唔驚嘅行動派！<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6qYyK1p89nU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6qYyK1p89nU&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=2f566df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6qYyK1p89nU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>前言：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地係<span style=\"color: red;\">先行者</span>，一班唔怕被解僱，願意為社會出多一份力既人。<br />\n<br />\n極權步步進逼，由解放軍出動，二噁英毒氣滿佈，到以武力攻擊校園，以屠殺為目標。雖然近期我們先後贏得區選，並獲人權法案簽署，然而我們距離五大訴求，以及清算警隊仍然有一段距離。同時，中共將會重新審視對香港的形勢，更劇烈的打壓將會重臨。今日再唔反抗，我們將會迎來最悲慘既結局---新疆般既種族清洗。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我正式呼籲各位無負擔/敢於犧牲參與「罷工宣言」行動，透過遞信俾老細/同事，甚至係工司群組內發放文宣，去正式宣佈無限期罷工，為其他仲有負擔既人做一個榜樣。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣做，除咗可以打破囚徒困境(因為已知有&quot;1&quot;個人肯罷)，亦可以令香港經濟呢個緊密既齒輪鬆脫。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一個人既罷工其實無大家想像如此無用：<br />\n香港既高物價高薪金令人手長期緊張，一個人既罷工會令整間公司運作減緩，公司運作放緩就會令其生意既合作夥伴受到影響；一環扣一環下，社會就會漸漸癱瘓。唔少人嘅職位雖然低但係對公司而言不可或缺。<br />\n</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2TbESVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2TbESVs.png&h=b96ab5c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CY6BaG8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCY6BaG8.png&h=3c2a29f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YBLRJ19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYBLRJ19.png&h=434439c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AA6xVu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AA6xVu.png&h=ed5c0238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pkrdXm9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpkrdXm9.png&h=9e6778b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YdmxttQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYdmxttQ.png&h=5649a2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ouTPvHa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FouTPvHa.png&h=902e003c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqrdXnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqrdXnb.png&h=c090afb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktXkCnb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktXkCnb.png&h=abeb62cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6yufrfx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yufrfx.png&h=e0ae4899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>點做更有效？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n行動：<br />\n1.發送文宣(whatsapp/email/打印)俾老細同事，宣佈你要罷工<br />\n2.嘗試與同事傾一傾而家處境有幾嚴峻，盡量說服佢地罷工<br />\n3.係社交媒體同朋友圈子內不停發佈，推post，務求令更多人知道呢件事<br />\n4.加入我地一齊宣傳<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NvR9vHF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNvR9vHF.jpg&h=37059b50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wjp7hnF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWjp7hnF.jpg&h=bfac634e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>得我罷咪變咗Condom？</strong></span></span><br />\n呢個問題就要問手足你願唔願意冒風險去營造一場公司罷工，定係下下都要等人，等工會帶？<br />\n前線手足有幾多人仲可以等咁耐？口講前線唔係Condom但係自己一啲犧牲都唔做？<br />\n只要多一個人全職投入抗爭，呢場抗爭就多一分勝算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請大家按自己能力入群！同時我們亦更加容易聯合到相同處境既人士！<br />\n1.第一梯隊：如果你願意做罷工敢炒隊，請去呢度：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/353CbNN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F353CbNN&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=5f768921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/353CbNN</a><br />\n2.第二梯隊：如果你公司有人做敢炒隊就會跟住罷工，請入呢度︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/37bMbXd\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F37bMbXd&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=971b8a35\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/37bMbXd</a><br />\n4.如果真係有好多人罷工/要有工會先罷工請入呢度︰<a href=\"http://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=7548ac2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n5.如果你只想得知最新消息請去公海︰<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2rHLbJV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rHLbJV&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cdxiqP1mjC8IHxs%2BzMkXvdI%3D&h=9ebbc8f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2rHLbJV</a>"},{"pid":"5da2f781519cebce446adb9780d96381a8475ac1","tid":1777827,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:27:34.000Z","msg":"【突發】保守黨侯選議員回信，稱英領手足為 【countrymen and women】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1777795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1777795</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9f1902d84c3f0980b69ea2025d401dbffa8e6afb","tid":1777827,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:27:45.000Z","msg":"【行動post】聽日集會有不反啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1777805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1777805</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bd9f26e16dded9f96e758392ebc94a691ed63ee4","tid":1777827,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:27:49.000Z","msg":"sorry 借個位<im